Cognate with {{cog|la|adagium}}, {{m|la|prōdigium}}, {{cog|grc|ἠμί||to say}}, {{cog|xcl|ասեմ||to say}}, and {{cog|ine-toc-pro|*āks-||to announce, proclaim, instruct}}. See also {{m|la|negō}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{la-IPA|aiō}}

===Verb===
{{la-verb|irreg|aiō}}

# I say, I assert, I say yes, I say no, I affirm, I [[assent]]
#* '''1826''', [[w:Stanislaus Julien|Stanislaus Julien]] translating [[w:Mencius|Mencius]] as [https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=_qpp_gwHlfEC&printsec=frontcover ''Meng Tseu''], [https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=_qpp_gwHlfEC&pg=PA46 p. 46]:
